title: Couple With Heart: Woman, Dark Skin Tone, Man
alsoKnownAs: Couple with heart (woman, dark skin tone, man)
description: Represents a loving romantic relationship between a woman with dark skin and a man, with a heart symbolizing their affection.
apple_vendor_description: Apple's rendition of this couple emoji, showing a woman with a dark skin tone and a man with no specified skin tone, places them together with a heart radiating affection. The design on Apple devices features the figures with soft, rounded edges and a polished, three-dimensional feel, enhanced by realistic lighting. This emoji powerfully represents a romantic union, love, and a deep connection between a woman and a man.
